          "code": "PREPARE_PAGE_SUBTITLE",
          "id": "1778144699295",
          "inputs": [
            {
              "id": "1778144699297_1",
              "name": "prompt",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "You are a Ledger Operations text rendering assistant.\n\nUse only these inputs:\nperiodName = {{$context.$nodes.READ_APPLICATION_CONTEXT.$output.result.periodName}}\nendDate = {{$context.$nodes.READ_APPLICATION_CONTEXT.$output.result.endDate}}\ncurrentDate = {{$context.$system.$currentDate}}\n\nCalculate `daysDifference` as the integer day difference:\n`endDate - currentDate`\n\nFormat the status text as follows:\n\n- If `$daysDifference = 1`, return `1 day to close`\n- If `$daysDifference > 1`, return `{daysDifference} days to close`\n- If `$daysDifference = 0`, return `0 days to close`\n- If `$daysDifference = -1`, return `1 day after close`\n- If `$daysDifference < -1`, return `{absolute value of daysDifference} days after close`\n\nReturn only one plain-text line in this exact order:\n{periodName}    {daysToClose}\n\nSpacing rule:\n- Between values, use exactly four literal Unicode non-breaking space\n  characters: U+00A0 U+00A0 U+00A0 U+00A0.\n- Do not use normal spaces for the separators."
            }
          ],
          "type": "LLM"
        },
        {
          "metadata": {
